data.description: *** PRICED TO SELL****  Discover tranquil living in this beautiful 3 bed/2.5 bath tucked away in a quiet neighborhood. This property offers the perfect retreat for those seeking serenity and natural beauty, situated between Canton and Ellijay, yet conveniently located minutes away from the bustling downtown Jasper and I-515. You'll enjoy sipping your morning coffee on the private back porch while listening to the birds and enjoying the beautiful scenery. Step inside to find an open concept interior boasting brand-new floors and paint throughout. The master bedroom provides a relaxing escape, while two additional well-appointed bedrooms offer versatility for a home office or guest quarters with a Jack and Jill bathroom. This home is well constructed with upgrades including granite counter tops, kitchen backsplash, ceiling fans in secondary bedrooms, luxury vinyl flooring, shaker style cabinetry, ample deck and upgraded landscaping. Private fenced in backyard borders wooded green space. Floor plan includes basement that's ready to finish and make your own. A 2-car garage, with added garage door opener and ample storage space. Like new condition! Move in ready! Motivated seller; bring all offers!
